        "created_at": "2018-03-25T01:06:51.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi Larry, it was with '08 Dujac Echezeaux, '05 Mongeard-Mugneret Grands Echezeaux, '00 Potel Latricieres, '07 Faiveley Corton CdC, '06 Boisset CdlR, '11 Geantet-Pansiot Charmes-Chambertin and '08 Maison de Grand Esprit Echezeaux La Belle Voisine.</p>\n<p>Cheers<br>\nJeremy</p>",
